    "description": "Suven Pharmaceuticals, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Radiologist for our Patna operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Suven Pharmaceuticals:\nSuven Pharmaceuticals is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Suven Pharmaceuticals!",
